    public abstract class GraphAlgorithmDelegatingGraph<IN_K,IN_VV,IN_EV,OUT_K,OUT_VV,OUT_EV>
extends Object
implements GraphAlgorithm<IN_K,IN_VV,IN_EV,Graph<OUT_K,OUT_VV,OUT_EV>>
    A GraphAlgorithm transforms an input Graph into an output of type T. A GraphAlgorithmDelegatingGraph wraps the resultant Graph with a delegating proxy object. The delegated object can be replaced when the same algorithm is run on the same input with a mergeable configuration. This allows algorithms to be composed of implicitly reusable algorithms without publicly sharing intermediate DataSets.
